Streme, accessible at https://farcaster.xyz/streme and also referred to as streamm.xyz, is a Farcaster Mini App designed to function as a “YouTube-like” video client tailored for the decentralized social network. It allows users to share, view, and potentially create video content, including private videos and live streams, secured by cryptographic keys. Streme integrates with Farcaster’s infrastructure to deliver a seamless video-sharing experience, leveraging the protocol’s support for streamable video formats and community-driven engagement.

